    "Results Quantitative EvaluationTables 1 and 2 provide the quantitative results of the IU X-RAY and MIMIC-CXR test sets, respectively.",
    "The detailed results show that the ClinicalBLIP model exhibited robust performance when compared with other methods across the IU X-RAY and MIMIC-CXR data sets.",
